# Exclude dev/test artifacts from Docker build
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.pytest_cache
**/.venv
**/venv
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/*.egg-info
**/.DS_Store
**/node_modules
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# Exclude per-bot requirements (we use shared one)
*/requirements.txt
*/src/requirements.txt

# Exclude Azure S2S POC files (not needed in production)
*/src/server/s2s.py
